messages.content:
你是 marketting-planning-intent 项目的 attribute agent。
只归因当前单轮 intent-recognition 链路：request_normalization、intent_api_call、adapter_extraction、label_mapping；不要把 planning/SSE generation 的问题归入本项目。
优先使用 intent_contract_probe 定位 intent label、required slots/entities、confidence threshold、fallback policy 或 label_mapping 的当前证据差异。
只能输出 AttributeResult JSON 所需字段；证据不足时用 evidence_strength=none/weak 和 root_cause_hypothesis 表达缺口。
最终只输出 AttributeResult JSON 所需字段：expectation_attributions、suspected_locations、root_cause_hypothesis、evidence、evidence_strength。

## 输出约束：attribute 归因分析输出
你的输出必须是合法 JSON，且严格符合以下 JSON Schema：
```json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "expectation_attributions": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "$ref": "#/$defs/ExpectationAttribution"
      },
      "minItems": 1
    },
    "suspected_locations": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {}
    },
    "root_cause_hypothesis": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 1
    },
    "evidence": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {}
    },
    "evidence_strength": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 1
    }
  },
  "additionalProperties": false,
  "$defs": {
    "ExpectationAttribution": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "expectation_id": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "fulfillment_status": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "suspected_locations": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {}
        },
        "root_cause_hypothesis": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "evidence": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {}
        }
      },
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": [
        "expectation_id",
        "fulfillment_status"
      ]
    }
  },
  "required": [
    "expectation_attributions",
    "root_cause_hypothesis"
  ]
}
```

### 强约束
- 最终回答必须只包含一个 JSON object；不要输出 Markdown，不要使用 ```json 代码块，不要在 JSON 外输出解释、前缀或后缀。
- 最终回答首字符必须是 `{`，末字符必须是 `}`。
- JSON 字符串内部如需引用用户原词，禁止直接写未转义英文双引号；请使用中文引号“”或转义为 `\"`。
- 必须包含 `required` 列表中的所有字段。
- 每个字段值必须匹配 schema 中的类型。
- 以下字段必须非空（空字符串/空数组/空对象/None 均视为不合规，会被阻断）：['expectation_attributions', 'root_cause_hypothesis']
- `additionalProperties: false`：禁止输出 schema 未定义的字段。
- 禁止把 schema 里的类型描述符（如 "string"）原样当作内容填进去——每个字段必须填入真实内容。

{
  "expectation_attributions": [
    {
      "expectation_id": "意图标签识别必须为customer_portrait",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": [
        "adapter_extraction",
        "label_mapping"
      ],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "adapter_extraction阶段将原始意图编码“4001”错误映射为“other”，未产生期望的“customer_portrait”标签",
      "evidence": [
        {
          "extracted_output.intent": "other"
        },
        {
          "intent_contract_probe.evidence_intent": "4001"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "必须抽取出目标实体“上个月成交客户”",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": [
        "adapter_extraction",
        "intent_api_call"
      ],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "意图识别失败导致target_value未抽取；若意图正确，实体抽取模块可能正常返回“上个月成交客户”",
      "evidence": [
        {
          "extracted_output.target_value": null
        },
        {
          "intent_evidence.entities": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "置信度应不低于0.95",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": [
        "adapter_extraction",
        "intent_api_call"
      ],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "置信度0.5远低于0.95，源于意图映射失败导致置信度评估降低；原始API可能因未正确识别而返回低置信度",
      "evidence": [
        {
          "extracted_output.confidence": 0.5
        },
        {
          "reference_contract.confidence": 0.95
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "回退策略应正确，避免误判为other",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": [
        "adapter_extraction",
        "label_mapping"
      ],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "意图误判为“other”，可能是映射缺失或回退策略不当将可识别意图错误归为“other”",
      "evidence": [
        {
          "extracted_output.intent": "other",
          "subIntent": "其他意图"
        },
        {
          "intent_evidence.fallback": false
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "意图分发边界应准确映射到customer_portrait流程",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": [
        "label_mapping",
        "adapter_extraction"
      ],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "最终intent为“other”，无法映射到customer_portrait分析流程；问题源于上游意图识别错误",
      "evidence": [
        {
          "extracted_output.intent": "other"
        },
        {
          "reference_contract.intent": "customer_portrait"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "intent_contract",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": [
        "adapter_extraction"
      ],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "整体意图识别合同未满足，核心是意图标签错误导致所有判定失败",
      "evidence": [
        {
          "judge_result.reasoning_summary": "当前单轮意图识别未满足 reference contract：query=能不能帮我分析一下，上个月成交的客户主要都是些什么类型的人，expected_intent=customer_portrait，actual_intent=other，confidence=0.5，min_confidence=None，失败项=['intent']，整体判定为 incorrect。"
        },
        {
          "intent_contract_probe.intent_match": false
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "suspected_locations": [
    "adapter_extraction (in app/workflow/steps/intent_recognition.py)",
    "label_mapping (projects/marketting-planning-intent/intent.py:INTENT_MAPPING)"
  ],
  "root_cause_hypothesis": "在intent-recognition链路中，adapter_extraction阶段未能将API返回的原始意图编码“4001”正确映射为期望的“customer_portrait”，而错误地映射为“other”并附带低置信度0.5，导致所有下游期望（意图标签、实体抽取、置信度、回退策略、分发边界）连锁失败。label_mapping阶段也未纠正此错误。",
  "evidence": [
    {
      "stage": "adapter_extraction",
      "output": {
        "intent": "other",
        "confidence": 0.5
      }
    },
    {
      "intent_contract_probe": {
        "actual_intent": "other",
        "evidence_intent": "4001",
        "intent_match": false
      }
    },
    {
      "runtime_checks": {
        "status": "failed",
        "actual_mapping": "other",
        "raw_intent": null
      }
    },
    {
      "judge_result.reasoning_summary": "intent incorrect"
    }
  ],
  "evidence_strength": "high"
}

